Package: guidelinely
Type: Package
Title: R Client for the Guidelinely Environmental Guidelines API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides programmatic access to the Guidelinely API 
    (https://guidelines.1681248.com), an environmental guideline calculation and 
    search API. Calculate guideline values for chemical parameters in various 
    environmental media (water, soil, sediment) based on environmental context 
    (pH, hardness, temperature). Search parameters, query metadata, and access 
    comprehensive guideline sources through a clean R interface.
